{"tid":1092660,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[7月新番]擅長捉弄人的高木同學 2期 からかい上手の高木さん集中討論(2)","createTime":"2019-04-05T04:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T09:13:09.000Z","uid":3020,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c447be3d4b77e87460ce350c045f06c2005f036","tid":1092660,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kuRQMHW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkuRQMHW.png&h=bb398d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PGwhnkF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPGwhnkF.jpg&h=39dd4c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwMQtd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwMQtd4.jpg&h=dab8e16f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事簡介:<br />\n普通的男子中學生西片，和一位古靈精怪的女生高木坐在一起，高木經長捉弄著遲鈍的西片，把他耍得團團轉，教室後面是他們小動作的空間。儘管西片總想著報復回去，但卻始終在高木層出不窮的點子面前以失敗告終。本作品便是敘述兩人打打鬧鬧的日常校園生活。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF：<br />\n原作：山本崇一朗「からかい上手の高木さん」「あしたは土曜日」（小学館「ゲッサン」刊）<br />\n監督：赤城博昭<br />\nシリーズ構成：横手美智子<br />\nキャラクターデザイン：髙野 綾、総作画監督：茂木琢次・近藤奈都子、音楽：堤博明<br />\nアニメーション制作：シンエイ動画<br />\nOP：「言わないけどね。」大原ゆい子（TOHO animation RECORDS）<br />\n<br />\nCAST：<br />\n高木さん：高橋李依<br />\n西片：梶 裕貴<br />\nミナ：小原好美<br />\nユカリ：M・A・O<br />\nサナエ：小倉唯<br />\n中井：内田雄馬<br />\n真野：小岩井ことり<br />\n高尾：岡本信彦<br />\n木村：落合福嗣<br />\n田辺先生：田所陽向<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://anime1.me/category//2018年冬季/擅長捉弄人的高木同學\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanime1.me%2Fcategory%2F%2F2018%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%2F%E6%93%85%E9%95%B7%E6%8D%89%E5%BC%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E9%AB%98%E6%9C%A8%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=3b13178d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://anime1.me/category//2018年冬季/擅長捉弄人的高木同學</a><br />\n1期<br />\nPV2：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4VJra3sLMg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg4VJra3sLMg&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=7d600a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g4VJra3sLMg</a><br />\n<br />\nPV1：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KwUghPuqNAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKwUghPuqNAU&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=3864543e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KwUghPuqNAU</a></div><br />\n<br />\n2期<br />\nPV1：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eKiYU9d03qc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeKiYU9d03qc&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=1be647e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eKiYU9d03qc</a><br />\n<br />\n[7月新番]擅長捉弄人的高木同學 2期 TVアニメ『からかい上手の高木さん２』PV第1弾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1086094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1086094</a><br />\n擅長捉弄人的高木同學からかい上手の高木さん新宣傳圖片<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1084475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1084475</a>"},{"pid":"4f83cae9aa122d734783ecaee1650f721e673c63","tid":1092660,"uid":31542,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"4月就開定7月嘅番 點同你玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7342032e63b8a89e8691827fb28fecd9333beb","tid":1092660,"uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f83cae9aa122d734783ecaee1650f721e673c63","tid":1092660,"uid":31542,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"4月就開定7月嘅番 點同你玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/522603/